SUMMARY:Spring Renewal with Ryan Bright: Sound Frequency Healing with Gongs & Vibrations
DESCRIPTION:Spring Renewal is calling… your monthly sound reset with Ryan Bright is HERE.  \n\n\n\nAfter two powerful sessions kicking off 2026 (January’s deep Winter Resonance + February’s pre-Valentine glow that left everyone floating)\, we’re flowing into spring with the 3rd Sound Frequency Journey.  90 minutes of immersive healing vibes: powerful gongs\,  harmonicas\, voice & elemental frequencies for total release + realignment.   \n\n\n\nNo experience needed\, just your mat (or blanket) and an open heart.  
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/spring-renewal-with-ryan-bright-sound-frequency-healing-with-gongs-vibrations/
LOCATION:Inspire Wellness Collective\, 226 North Arch Street\, Lancaster\, Pennsylvania\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Classes and Workshops
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/Red-and-White-Modern-Meet-Our-New-Team-LinkedIn-Post.jpg
END:VEVENT
