SUMMARY:4th Annual Community Easter Egg Hunt
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Historic Lions Club along with partners SoWe\, Lancaster Moose Lodge 299\, and SDoL hold this egg hunt with 5000+ eggs filled with candy and toys at Culltion Park. We provide free prepackaged food\, books\, and prizes to 250+ children. We will also have food trucks on site for purchase.
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/4th-annual-community-easter-egg-hunt/
LOCATION:Culliton Park\, 200 S. Water Street\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Family Fun,Free Events and Activites,Holiday
