DESCRIPTION:Time to get outside with The Big Bloom Market! \n\n\n\nWe’ve been cooped up for too long. Join us for a free outdoor market. Shop vendors selling art\, vintage clothing\, jewelry\, and more. Family and dog friendly! \n\n\n\nDATE: MARCH 29THTIME: 12pm-4pmLOCATION: Across the street from Hempfield Apothetique @ 100 W Walnut St\, Lancaster\, PA \n\n\n\nStick around for the SLAP IT! Graffiti 21+ event from 4pm-9pm inside The Lounge!
