SUMMARY:Video Game Day at The Lancaster Science Factory
DESCRIPTION:We’re partnering with the Lancaster Rec Esports program for a day of video game design and play! Compete in popular games like Super Smash Brothers™ and Mario Kart™. Players can test their skills\, cheer on friends\, and experience the excitement of esports in a welcoming\, supportive environment. \n\n\n\nVisitors of all ages can also participate in our Play for Impact Video Game Design Workshops. Participants will design\, develop\, and test their own video game using Scratch\, a block-based programming tool. \n\n\n\nThis event is free with admission to the Lancaster Science Factory.
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/video-game-day-at-the-lancaster-science-factory/
